## Wiki (Persistent Memory)

**Vault:** `obsidian-vault/` (Obsidian vault in project root)
**Schema:** `obsidian-vault/wiki-schema.md`
**Compiler:** `karpaty-memory/scripts/compile.py`

### Quick Reference
- **Start of session:** read `obsidian-vault/index.md` + last 5 entries of `obsidian-vault/log.md`
- **Manual ingest:** `uv run --directory karpaty-memory python scripts/compile.py`
- **Auto-compile:** flush.py triggers compile.py after 18:00 if daily log changed or unprocessed raw files exist
- **User says "ingest" / "обработай":** run compile.py or use the wiki-ingest skill
- **User says "remember this" / "note this":** create or update the relevant wiki page immediately
- **User says "lint the wiki":** `uv run --directory karpaty-memory python scripts/lint.py`

### Source Types
| Source | Nature | Lifecycle |
|--------|--------|-----------|
| `raw/` | Manual (devlog, articles, transcripts) | Immutable — never modified or deleted |
| `daily/` | Auto-generated (session summaries from hooks) | Ephemeral — deleted after compilation |

### Structure
```
obsidian-vault/
├── index.md           ← READ FIRST. Single unified catalog of all wiki pages.
├── log.md             ← Append-only activity log.
├── wiki-schema.md     ← Full schema (ingest/query/lint rules).
├── daily/             ← Ephemeral session logs (deleted after compile).
├── raw/               ← Immutable source documents.
│   └── assets/        ← Downloaded images.
├── wiki/
│   ├── architecture/  ← System design, data flows.
│   ├── decisions/     ← Design decisions with rationale.
│   ├── bugs/          ← Notable bugs, root causes, fixes.
│   ├── features/      ← Feature design docs.
│   ├── concepts/      ← Domain concepts, atomic knowledge.
│   ├── operations/    ← Deployment, CI/CD.
│   └── connections/   ← Cross-cutting insights.
```
